	"packageName": "@anvilkit/plugin-ai-copilot",
	"readme": [
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "# @anvilkit/plugin-ai-copilot\n\nHeadless AI copilot for Anvilkit Studio. The plugin caches a per-session\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`AiGenerationContext`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " derived from the host's Puck config, calls a\nhost-supplied "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`generatePage(prompt, ctx)`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " function, validates the\nresponse with "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@anvilkit/validator`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", and dispatches the result atomically\nvia "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`setData`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ".\n\n> **Status:** alpha. API may change before "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`1.0`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ".\n\n## Install\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```bash\npnpm add @anvilkit/plugin-ai-copilot\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\n## Usage\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```ts\nimport { createAiCopilotPlugin } from \"@anvilkit/plugin-ai-copilot\";\nimport { puckConfig } from \"./puck-config\";\n\nconst aiCopilot = createAiCopilotPlugin({\n  puckConfig,\n  generatePage: async (prompt, ctx) => {\n    const response = await fetch(\"/api/ai/generate\", {\n      method: \"POST\",\n      body: JSON.stringify({ prompt, availableComponents: ctx.availableComponents }),\n    });\n    return response.json();\n  },\n  timeoutMs: 30_000,\n  forwardCurrentData: true,\n});\n\n<Studio plugins={[aiCopilot]} ... />\n\nawait aiCopilot.runGeneration(\"Build a hero with a CTA\");\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\n## Security model\n\n- The plugin **never sees credentials**. API keys, auth headers, and\n  endpoints belong to the host backend.\n- "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`generatePage`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is invoked with exactly two arguments: "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`(prompt, ctx)`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ".\n- Every LLM response runs through "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`validateAiOutput`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " before being\n  dispatched.\n- The dispatch is atomic.\n\n## License\n\nMIT."
		}
	],
